xt-date">November 12, 2020</span></div></div></div></a><!-- wilson_search.renderable --><a class="teaser" data-type="blog-post" href="/blog-post/what-will-biden-presidency-mean-korean-peninsula"><div class="teaser-image"><img src="/sites/default/files/styles/teaser/public/media/uploads/images/AP_2020-11-10-BlogImage_StateDepartment.jpg" alt="Joe Biden stands at a podium delivering a speech in front of U.S. and South Korean flags" width="100%" height="auto"></div><div class="teaser-content"><div class="teaser-top-meta"><div class="teaser-type">Blog post</div><div class="teaser-topic">U.S. Elections</div></div><div class="teaser-title"><span class="teaser-title-text">What Will a Biden Presidency Mean for the Korean Peninsula?</span></div><div class="teaser-byline"><div class="teaser-byline-text"><span class="teaser-byline-text-plain">By&nbsp;</span><span class="teaser-byline-text-author">Jean H. Lee</span><span class="teaser-byline-text-plain">&nbsp;on&nbsp;</span><span class="teaser-byline-text-date">November 10, 2020</span></div></div></div></a><!-- wilson_search.renderable --></div></div></div></div></main><footer class="site-footer"><div class="site-footer-top"><div class="site-footer-top-inner"><div class="site-footer-column"><a class="site-footer-logo" href="/"><img src="/themes/custom/wilson/assets/images/footer-logo.svg" alt="Wilson Center" width="100%" height="auto"></a><p class="site-footer-location -serif">One Woodrow Wilson Plaza<br>1300 Pennsylvania Ave. NW<br>Washington, DC 20004-3027</p><a class="site-footer-visit" href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/The+Wilson+Center/@38.8934628,-77.0325588,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x89b7b79762f518d1:0x3e73088a9489b574!8m2!3d38.8934586!4d-77.0303701" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Visit the Wilson Center</a><div class="site-footer-phone"><div class="site-footer-phone-label">Phone:</div><a class="site-footer-phone-link" href="tel:202-691-4000">(202) 691-4000</a></div><a class="site-footer-contact" href="/contac